"attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Enhanced reporting","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Agriculture shall develop and implement the system required under paragraph (2)(A) of section 251(g) of the Agricultural Marketing Act of 1946 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1636/g"},"text":"7 U.S.C. 1636(g)","children":[],"tail":"), as amended by paragraph (1), not later than one year after the date on which the Secretary determines sufficient funds have been appropriated pursuant to subsection (c) ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/2113"},"text":"122 Stat. 2113","children":[],"tail":"]."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"“(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Current system","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding the amendment made by paragraph (1), the Secretary shall continue to use the information format for disseminating information under subtitle B [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1635"},"text":"7 U.S.C. 1635","children":[],"tail":" et seq.] of the Agricultural Marketing Act of 1946 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1621"},"text":"7 U.S.C. 1621","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) in effect on the date of the enactment of this Act ["},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-06-18"},"text":"June 18, 2008","children":[],"tail":"] at least until the date that is two years after the date on which the Secretary makes the determination referred to in subparagraph (A).”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"[","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":" enacted identical provisions. "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4/a"},"text":"section 4(a) of Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s8701"},"text":"section 8701 of this title","children":[],"tail":".]"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
